---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Terms of Service</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Terms and Conditions</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>
    
    <!-- Language Navigation -->
    <nav class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8" role="navigation" aria-label="Language selection">
      <span class="text-sm text-gray" title="Current language: ENG" aria-current="page">ENG</span>
      <a href="/de/tos" class="text-sm text-gray underline hover:text-gray-light transition-colors" title="Switch to German" aria-label="View terms in German">DEU</a>
      <a href="/bs/tos" class="text-sm text-gray underline hover:text-gray-light transition-colors" title="Switch to Bosnian" aria-label="View terms in Bosnian">BOS</a>
    </nav>
    
    <div class="flex w-full m-0 flex-col justify-evenly px-8">
      <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-3 mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-4">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">1. About Our Service</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          Japodium is a mobile application and website that serves as an <strong>intermediary booking platform</strong> 
          connecting users with local tourist agencies, extreme sport operators, and licensed tour guides who offer 
          recreational activities such as rafting tours, quad riding, bike rentals, guided city tours, and similar services.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">2. Important Disclaimer - We Are Not a Service Provider</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          <strong>CRITICAL NOTICE:</strong> Japodium does NOT directly provide, operate, or sell any recreational services, 
          tours, or activities. We act solely as a reservation platform that facilitates contact between users and 
          third-party service providers. All recreational activities, tours, pricing, content, and offers displayed 
          in our app are determined, operated, and provided exclusively by independent third-party agencies and operators.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">3. Reservation Process</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          When you submit a reservation request through our app, the following process occurs:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light ml-6 mt-2 list-disc">
          <li>Your reservation details (name, email, phone, participants, date) are sent to both you and our admin at info@japodium.com</li>
          <li>Our agent will contact you for confirmation purposes only</li>
          <li>We connect you directly with the relevant third-party service provider or tour guide</li>
          <li>From that point forward, all interactions, arrangements, and transactions occur directly between you and the service provider</li>
          <li>Japodium is not involved in the actual service delivery, payment processing, or any aspect of your experience</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          <strong>NO LIABILITY:</strong> Japodium, its owners, developers, and agents are NOT responsible for:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light ml-6 mt-2 list-disc">
          <li>Any injuries, damages, losses, or accidents that may occur during any recreational activity</li>
          <li>The quality, safety, or condition of any services provided by third-party operators</li>
          <li>Inaccuracies in pricing, descriptions, or availability of offered services</li>
          <li>Cancellations, delays, or changes to scheduled activities</li>
          <li>The conduct, qualifications, or licensing status of third-party service providers</li>
          <li>Any disputes between users and service providers</li>
          <li>Payment issues, refund policies, or financial transactions with service providers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">5. Extreme Sport Activities Warning</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          <strong>RISK ACKNOWLEDGMENT:</strong> Many activities available through our platform may include extreme sports 
          or physically challenging activities that carry inherent risks. These activities may not be appropriate for all 
          ages, fitness levels, or individuals with certain medical conditions. By using our reservation service, you acknowledge that:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light ml-6 mt-2 list-disc">
          <li>You participate in all activities at your own risk</li>
          <li>You are responsible for assessing your own fitness and suitability for any activity</li>
          <li>You should consult medical professionals if you have health concerns</li>
          <li>You will follow all safety instructions provided by the service providers</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">6. Service Provider Selection</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          While we make reasonable efforts to feature only reputable tourist agencies, sport operators, and licensed guides, 
          we do not guarantee or warranty the qualifications, licensing status, safety standards, or quality of any third-party 
          service provider. Users are responsible for conducting their own due diligence regarding service providers.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">7. User Responsibilities</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          As a user of our platform, you agree to:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light ml-6 mt-2 list-disc">
          <li>Provide accurate information in all reservation requests</li>
          <li>Communicate directly with service providers regarding terms, conditions, and payments</li>
          <li>Read and understand the terms and conditions of each service provider</li>
          <li>Take full responsibility for your participation in any booked activities</li>
          <li>Release Japodium from any claims related to your use of third-party services</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">8. App Usage Terms</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          This application is provided free of charge for informational and reservation facilitation purposes only. 
          The app does not require user registration and is available to users of all ages. We reserve the right to 
          modify or discontinue the service at any time without notice.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">9. Governing Law</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          These terms are governed by applicable local laws. Any disputes arising from your use of third-party services 
          must be resolved directly with the relevant service provider.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 text-gray-light">10. Contact Information</h2>
        <p class="text-md lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light">
          For questions about these terms or our reservation facilitation service, contact us at:
          <a class="underline" href="mailto:info@japodium.com">info@japodium.com</a>
        </p>
        
        <p class="text-md text-center lg:text-left leading-relaxed text-slate-500 text-gray-light mt-6">
          <strong>By using our app and reservation service, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to these terms.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="w-full justify-self-end text-center mt-16 my-4">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="text-center text-sm text-gray underline hover:text-gray-light active:text-gray-light"
          >Homepage</a
        >
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray mt-2">
          <a href="/privacy" class="text-center text-sm text-gray underline hover:text-gray-light active:text-gray-light">Privacy</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray mt-2">
          <a href="/tos" class="text-center text-sm text-gray underline hover:text-gray-light active:text-gray-light">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
        <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray mt-2">
          Copyright Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Japodium. All rights reserved.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
